<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>FUNdusky | Everything fun in Sandusky</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Everything fun in Sandusky. On the water, family fun, nightlife, and attractions." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #0c2d68;
      --navy-dark: #081d45;
      --orange: #f29a38;
      --orange-dark: #de8521;
      --bg: #f5f9ff;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --text: #1c2333;
      --muted: #5f6b7a;
      --shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      --radius: 18px;
      --max: 1120px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 90vh;
      background: url("images/hero-bg.jpg") center/cover no-repeat;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), 900px);
      padding: 40px 0 80px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
      max-width: 720px;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--orange-dark);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: #fff;
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }

    .section {
      padding: 64px 0;
    }

    .section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      color: var(--navy-dark);
    }

    .section p.lead {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 auto 32px;
      max-width: 700px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .card img {
      height: 220px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .card-content {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 1.35rem;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .category-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .category-card img {
      height: 240px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .category-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,29,69,0.78), rgba(8,29,69,0.15));
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .category-overlay div {
      color: #fff;
    }

    .category-overlay h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
    }

    .category-overlay p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .footer-space {
      height: 30px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .grid-2 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 82vh;
      }

      .card img,
      .category-card img {
        height: 210px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Everything fun in Sandusky</h1>
      <p>On the water, family fun, nightlife, and attractions — all in one place.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#categories" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Activities</a>
        <a href="#trending" class="btn btn-secondary">See What’s Trending</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="categories">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Explore by Category</h2>
      <p class="lead">Choose what kind of day you want to have — from jet skis and boats to bowling, bars, and Cedar Point.</p>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <a href="water.html" class="card category-card">
          <img src="images/boat.PNG" alt="On the Water" />
          <div class="category-overlay">
            <div>
              <h3>On the Water</h3>
              <p>Jet skis, boat rentals, sunset cruises, and more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="card category-card">
          <img src="images/family.jpg" alt="Family Fun" />
          <div class="category-overlay">
            <div>
              <h3>Family Fun</h3>
              <p>Bowling, go-karts, putt putt, and activities for everyone.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="card category-card">
          <img src="images/nightlife.jpg" alt="Nightlife" />
          <div class="category-overlay">
            <div>
              <h3>Nightlife</h3>
              <p>Bars, live music, late nights, and packed rooms.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="card category-card">
          <img src="images/attractions.jpg" alt="Attractions" />
          <div class="category-overlay">
            <div>
              <h3>Attractions</h3>
              <p>Cedar Point and the can’t-miss Sandusky experience.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="trending">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Trending Right Now</h2>
      <p class="lead">The stuff people actually want to do when they get here.</p>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <a href="water.html" class="card">
          <img src="images/jetski.jpg" alt="Jet Ski Rentals" />
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Jet Ski Rentals</h3>
            <p>Get out on Lake Erie and ride your own Sea-Doo for a real Sandusky day.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="water.html" class="card">
          <img src="images/boat.PNG" alt="Boat Rentals and Sunset Cruises" />
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Boat Rentals & Sunset Cruises</h3>
            <p>Relax, cruise, and catch the best views on the water with your group.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="footer-space"></div>

</body>
</html>
